Today our heroes find themselves traveling through the forest,
heading towards Cinnabar Island, the site of the next Pokemon Gym.
There Ash hopes to win his seventh Pokemon badge.
However this forest is not as peaceful as it seems.
-He looks like a thief to me.
Show that thief who is boss.
Were not going to hurt you.
Just what do you think you are doing, interfering with us?
But we were just trying to help you
capture that dangerous thief before he got way.
Hes a police officer training our canine police unit.
the Growlithe will drive away enemies by barking and biting.
I guess that must make Growlithe a perfect Pokemon for the police to use.
These Growlithe pups are so well-trained.
They Are not going to bite us, are they?
The Growlithe will not bite unless I order them to attack.
These people are our new friends.
Look, a whole pack of police-trained Pokemon.
The boss would certainly love that.
Yeah, but who knows if their bark is worse than their bite?
I believe I have the perfect plan for capturing those puppies.
I hope you will be able to eat something.
I guess that is not a problem.
Did you see the way that Growlithe tackled that guy, Brock?

You cannot expect Pikachu to attack somebody like that.
I bet you never even thought about how badly Pikachu could have been hurt.
Having a Pokemon take on an armed opponent
is very, very dangerous unless it has special training.
So far I Have only been using my Pokemon to battle
You Are thinking of something, Ash.
I hope you are not thinking of having Pikachu train

It Will make Pikachu even stronger.
Officer Jenny, will you train my Pikachu the way you train the Growlithe?
Well, this school is for training Growlithe.
We cannot admit just any Pokemon.
Maybe Pikachu just is not cut out for that kind of training.
You keep saying you want to become
the worlds best Pokemon breeder, do not you, Brock?
Well, sure, of course I do.
Well, I want to be the worlds best Pokemon trainer
and I also want my Pikachu to be the best Pokemon it can possibly be.
Well, if you really want your Pikachu to be the best,
why do not you bring your Pikachu down to our training class tomorrow?
Well, its time for our class.
Its time for you to start your training class.
Okay, first well test you out on the obstacle course.
Let Us show them what you can do.
-Do Not let that Growlithe beat you.
Actually, Pikachu will not be the only one running this race
-because you have to run too, Ash. -Me?
Ash, a master will never be respected
if he will not do something he asks his own Pokemon to do.
Ill be running too, so let us get started, shall we, Ash?
Heh, looks like Ash is having some second thoughts.
I wonder if this police training will be too tough.
-How are we going to get past it?
if they can do it, we can do it too.
-This training is tougher than I thought.
-Now we have to climb this thing?
This police canine training sure is tough.
Are you still going to go through with it?
Of course I Am going through with it because I want Pikachu to be the best.
But do not you think Pikachus a great Pokemon just the way it is?
Yeah, Pikachu's great but I want it to be just as tough as Growlithe.
That Is what you want too, is not it, Pikachu?
Hey, what is going on here?
To protect the world from devastation.
To unite all peoples within our nation.
To denounce the evils of truth and love.
To extend our reach to the stars above.
Team rocket blasts off at the speed of light.
Surrender now or prepare to fight.
They would not try to steal these Pokemon.
They must be crazy, breaking into a school for police canine.
Is Not that kind of like saying: Please arrest me?
These police Pokemon really give me the creeps.
Cannot we steal some Pokemon that are more cat-friendly?
We can do anything once we get that pack of obedient Growlithe.
They Will do whatever we command.
They Will rob banks whenever we see them.
They Will steal artworks from every museum.
Well be the richest criminals of all time!
The queen, the king, the cat of crime!
Luckily your dream will not come true.
These police Growlithe would never do anything to break the law.
Now those Growlithe will not be able to use their noses.
What kind of gas is this?
I sound like one of the chipmunks.
That gas they just sprayed makes your voice get high and squeaky.
Yes, were certainly hitting a career high note.
I do not know what you are planning,
but I Am placing you under arrest for trespassing.
The Growlithe cannot understand Jennys order now that her voice is changed.
If these Growlithe cannot use their sense of smell
and they cannot understand Jennys orders, they are useless as police Pokemon.
-Shall we move on to phase two?
And now for one more change.
This synthesizer will make me sound just like Officer Jenny.
What Is wrong with all of you?
That Is not me, that is Team Rocket.
All right, Growlithe, listen to me.
I want you to place that woman under house arrest.
And just how are you going to stop us, squeaky?
Why do not we teach them all a lesson before we go?
Well use our Pokemon to battle them.
Do Not let the bad criminals get away from Growlithe.
I want you to get in the car with these Growlithe.
That may sound like me but its Team Rocket.
My voice does not sound that messed up.
Ash and Pikachu recognize what is in each others hearts,
so Pikachu cannot be fooled by somebody using a fake voice.
Growlithe, get that Pikachu and its trainer now.
Quit fooling around and get them.
-Please, tell me what is wrong, Pikachu.
You Are dizzy from using too much electricity.
Team Rocket are the bad guys.
Do Not lick her, attack her.
Do what we tell you, you dimwit dogs.
I told you do not get us, get them!
I knew this would not work.
I sure made a big mistake.
Pikachu does not have to train with a canine squad to be the perfect Pokemon.

Heh, Ill try to keep that in mind.
Well, keep up the good work, both of you.
Id like Brock to know what is in my heart.
Brocks so good-looking and hes so talented.
I just love him so much.
